OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FDry and bright in the north
OL,6,Fat first. Cloud and rain, some heavy,
OL,7,Fsoon spread northeast. The rain
OL,8,Fbecomes patchy during the afternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOutbreaks
OL,11,Fof locally heavy rain spread northeast
OL,12,FFriday. This clears to patchy and
OL,13,Fshowery rain Saturday. The rain then
OL,14,Fclears overnight to leave Sunday dry
OL,15,Fwith sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
